    <li>Support for MCS7832 based devices has been added to <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=mos&amp;sektion=4">mos(4)</a>.
    <li>Support for the Roland UM-ONE has been added to <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=umidi&amp;sektion=4">umidi(4)</a>. 
    <li>Support for the AMD Hudson-2 chipset has been added to <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=azalia&amp;sektion=4">azalia(4)</a> and <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=piixpm&amp;sektion=4">piixpm(4)</a>.
    <li>Support for NetMos NM9820 cardbus serial cards has been added to <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=com&amp;sektion=4">com(4)</a>. 
